  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Product Advisor",
  "description": "<p>1. Deliver engaging product and service presentations to generate customer interest and sales prospects</p><p>2. Assist in development and refinement unique selling point sales speeches based on product evaluation insights</p><p>3. Assist in gathering and analyzing market information to evaluate new and existing products for competitive positioning</p><p>4. Carry out the sales & marketing activities for new & existing products which include a range of dental, skincare, health & nutritious products</p><p>5. Identify interests and understand customer needs and requirements</p><p>6. Visit clinics, hospitals, medical centers & retail outlets to do product presentation and detailing.</p><p>7. Manage, service, and expand existing customer base. Acquire new accounts (Clinics & Retail)</p><p>8. Support the annual budgeting process by providing relevant sales and market data</p><p>9. Able to handle different types of personalities</p><p>10. Strong listening, communication, presentation, and social skills</p><p>11. Pleasant personality</p><p>12. Responsible, Result –oriented, and meticulous with strong analytical, organizational, and multi-tasking skills</p><p>13. Sales & customer service oriented</p><p>14. Fresh diploma graduate with a health science background especially dental hygiene, nursing, or pharmaceutical science.</p><p>15. Self-motivated, energetic, and independent with good interpersonal and communication skills (especially in English)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
